    <div id="europe" class="tab-content"><section class="card p-12 text-center bg-gray-50 border-dashed border-2 border-gray-300"><div class="text-4xl mb-4">ğŸš§</div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-600 mb-2">ì½˜í…ì¸  ì œì‘ ì˜ˆì •</h3></section></div>
    <div id="china" class="tab-content"><section class="card p-12 text-center bg-gray-50 border-dashed border-2 border-gray-300"><div class="text-4xl mb-4">ğŸš§</div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-600 mb-2">ì½˜í…ì¸  ì œì‘ ì˜ˆì •</h3></section></div>
    <div id="japan" class="tab-content"><section class="card p-12 text-center bg-gray-50 border-dashed border-2 border-gray-300"><div class="text-4xl mb-4">ğŸš§</div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-600 mb-2">ì½˜í…ì¸  ì œì‘ ì˜ˆì •</h3></section></div>

    <footer class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200 text-center text-slate-500 text-sm pb-12"><p>ğŸ”’ <strong>Confidential</strong> | Â© 2025 Dr.FORHAIR Strategic Planning Team</p></footer>
